Palʊla François Luambo Luanzo Makiadi kɛ [[Hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ|hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ loɖo ŋgʊ wiye pɩnaɣ [[1938]] kɛ Sona-Bata tɛtʊ taa, Koŋgo Pɛɛlɩzɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa nɛ ɛsɩ [[Aloma fenaɣ|aloma fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 12 wiye pɩnaɣ [[1989]] kɛ Mɔn-Godini tɛtʊ taa kɛ [[Pɛliziki|Pɛɛlɩziki]] ɛjaɖɛ taa ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 51. Ɛ-hɩla kɩsɛsɛna kɔyɔ: Franco de Mi Amor, Le Sorcier De La Guitare, Grand Maître Yorgho. 

[[File:Statue of Franco Luambo Makiadi unveiled in Kinshasa.jpg|thumb|Statue of Franco Luambo Makiadi unveiled in Kinshasa]]

François Luambo Luanzo Makiadi kɛ Koŋgo ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu teyu, payʊ nɛ ti-luɖu nɔɔyʊ.Palʊla François Luambo Luanzo Makiadi kɛ Sona Pata tɛtʊ taa kɛ [[Kɔŋgo Kinsasa|Koŋgoo Kinsasa]] ɛjaɖɛ taa. Payaɣ ɛ-caa se Joseph Emongo nɛ ɛlakɩ tʊmɩyɛ kɛ sulukuŋ kpayaɣ tʊmɩyɛ taa. E-ɖoo ñɔhɔkɩ kpɔnɔnaa nɛ ɛpɛdɩɣ kɩyakɩŋ nɩɩyɛ taa. 

